NOTICE REGARDING SOURCE MATERIAL

This skill is a personal knowledge distillation based on reading notes from:

  Jinpei Yagi (八木仁平). How to Find What You Want to Do (如何找到想做的事).
  Translated by 徐艺菊. China Machine Press (机械工业出版社), 2023.
  Originally published in Japanese as 世界一やさしい「やりたいこと」の見つけ方
  ― 人生のモヤモヤから解放される自己理解メソッド (KADOKAWA, 2020).

The skill file (SKILL.md), reference documents, and any other materials in this
repository are original works — personal summaries, structured notes, and
independently written content — created by the repository author.

This repository does not reproduce substantial portions of the original text.
